## DBsubject(Calculus - multivariable)
## DBchapter(Differentiation of multivariable functions)
## DBsection(Directional derivatives and the gradient)
## Institution(University of Michigan)
## Author(Gavin LaRose)
## Level(4)
## MO(1)
## TitleText1('Calculus')
